00:36:00.160 --> 00:36:02.980
So the really important
thing to remind ourselves

00:36:02.980 --> 00:36:07.440
about happiness is that it's
a high performance fuel.

00:36:07.440 --> 00:36:10.470
So a grand fallacy
of the idea I'll

00:36:10.470 --> 00:36:14.340
be happy when is, if we
wait for all that happiness

00:36:14.340 --> 00:36:17.370
