00:36:32.310 --> 00:36:36.000
stifle innovation or ambition,
at least in my own life.

00:36:36.000 --> 00:36:41.040
It reminds you how far
you've come and reminds you

00:36:41.040 --> 00:36:43.082
how far you have yet to go.

