it is, trying it.

00:40:38.920 --> 00:40:40.810
And then being
mindful of that beep.

00:40:40.810 --> 00:40:42.740
I think I kind of like this.

00:40:42.740 --> 00:40:46.260
And then tweaking it from there
is how you find your passions.

00:40:46.260 --> 00:40:52.410
And passions to me
are things, activities

00:40:52.410 --> 00:40:54.210
that we fall in love
with, just like we

00:40:54.210 --> 00:40:58.020
fall in love with a spouse
or a member of our family.

00:40:58.020 --> 00:41:02.230
